## About

This Vagrant script will setup a single-node SeqWare box configured to use the Oozie workflow engine.

## Installing 

Install Vagrant using the package from their site: http://www.vagrantup.com/

  vagrant plugin install vagrant-aws

## Configuration

Edit the Vagrantfile to include your AWS credentials.

## Running

This command brings up a SeqWare VM on Amazon:

  vagrant up --provider=aws

In case you need to re-run the provisioning script:

  # just test shell setup
  vagrant provision --provision-with shell

